Okay As in every Source i Give Codes For Running Server Here is This :
Source Run = @echo off color 0a title Starting... echo. echo TehDeScape is Running.. Server Status = ONLINE echo. cd ../bin title W00t v3! "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.7.0_05\bin\java.exe" palidino76/rs2/Server 43594 pause
Client HD Run :
@echo off java -classpath out/production/508" "HD;lib/hdlibs.jar;lib/substance.jar client 16 live live software members english game0 pause

Credits : Me 70% :) Rswd 30% :)
Hope you Liked This ;)
